Individual




Robert L. Chioini



Mr. Robert L. Chioini is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Rockwell Medical, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Oakland County Planning & Economic Development (California) and Medical Main Street.
Mr. Chioini was previously employed as Operations Director by Rockwell Medical Supplies LLC and Regional Sales Manager by Dial Medical of Florida, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Michigan State University.



