Robert L. Chioini 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at ROCKWELL MEDICAL INC, Robert L. Chioini  made $1,676,548 in total compensation.  Of this total $847,584 was received as a salary, $805,205 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $0 was awarded as stock and $23,759 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


