Business Information
															The group's principal activity is to manufacture and distribute hemodialysis concentrates, dialysis kits and other ancillary hemodialysis products to hemodialysis providers. The group has licensed an iron maintenance therapy for dialysis patients utilizing water soluble iron in dialysate. The ancillary products include on-off kits, sterile subclavian dressing change trays, arterial and venous blood tubing lines, fistula needles, intravenous administration sets, transducer protectors and dialyzers. The group's principal suppliers include archer daniels midland co., ashland inc., cargill inc., church & dwight co. Inc., morton salt company and nipro medical corporation.   
															






                       
